data.description:
**** BRAND NEW ROOF**** SELLER OFFERING $5k IN BUYER CONCESSIONS*** 

Welcome to 5212 Donegal Bay, where sellers are generously offering buyers a $5,000 incentive to buyers. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, spans 1,317 square feet, providing an inviting and spacious living space for you and your loved ones. Enhanced with a brand new roof, this charming starter home is perfectly situated just moments away from Fort Cavazos, ensuring a seamless connection for military families looking for proximity to the base.

Conveniently positioned off Clear Creek Road, this property combines the best of both worlds: accessibility to local amenities, such as shopping centers and restaurants, and the tranquility of a serene suburban environment.
